FFA bring out some best quality of gameplaying, discussion on mobility, buffing, strategy flourished once it started.  Now, with release of sleeper, interest of ST Talisma dragon have diminished, so even less highly competive mob in game now.  At this point, most people have a taste of FFA and have pretty good idea of what is, and how it affecting them. <br>
